snippet.title: Celebrities React To Johnny Depp Winning Over Amber Heard In Court
snippet.description:
Celebrities React To Johnny Depp Winning Over Amber Heard In Court
It's almost impossible to not talk about Johnny Depp and how his court case is "progressing" in its own way over the last few months. Because it seems that every other week or so there is a new motion, a new ruling on a matter, and so on and so forth and it can be a bit confusing to see where everything stands. Especially when you recall that this court case started years ago and isn't going to end until at LEAST 2022...if we're lucky. But aside from Heard and Depp, what are others saying about the current matter? We'll break it all down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at how celebs have been reacting to what's going on with the court case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Can you believe that so many have gotten involved in their own way over the years? Do you think that there are going to be more instances of these people standing up for Johnny Depp? Or, will things got a bit quieter as we get towards the actual court case? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
